cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.IR 

The paper proposes a method for automated segmentation of retinal lesions and optic disk in fundus images using a deep fully convolutional neural network for semantic segmentation. This involves computer vision (CV) techniques and machine learning (ML) algorithms, which are covered under the arXiv sub-categories cs.CV, cs.LG, and cs.AI. Additionally, the paper deals with medical imaging, which falls under the sub-categories cs.MM and cs.IR. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CV, followed by cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, and cs.IR.
